trans-unit.source: Provides a managed representation of a Win32 `OVERLAPPED` structure, including methods to transfer information from an Overlapped instance to a <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"></xref> structure.
trans-unit.target: Ger en hanterad representation av ett Win32 `OVERLAPPED` struktur, inklusive metoder för att överföra information från en Overlapped-instans till en <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"> </xref> struktur.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Pack%2A> and <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.UnsafePack%2A> methods transfer information from an Overlapped object to a <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> structure that can be passed to Win32 API functions for asynchronous file I/O.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Pack%2A>och <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.UnsafePack%2A>metoder Överför information från ett Overlapped objekt till en <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped>struktur som kan skickas till Win32 API-funktioner för asynkrona i/o-fil.</xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> </xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.UnsafePack%2A> </xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Pack%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Unpack%2A> method transfers information from a <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> structure to an instance of the Overlapped class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Unpack%2A>Metoden Överför information från en <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped>struktur för en instans av klassen Overlapped.</xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> </xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Unpack%2A>

trans-unit.source: Changes to the properties of an Overlapped object affect its associated <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> structure, and vice versa.
trans-unit.target: Egenskaperna för ett objekt Overlapped ändringar som påverkar dess associerade <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped>struktur, och vice versa.</xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new, empty instance of the <xref href="System.Threading.Overlapped"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny, tom instans av den <xref href="System.Threading.Overlapped"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Threading.Overlapped"></xref> class with the specified file position, the 32-bit integer handle to an event that is signaled when the I/O operation is complete, and an interface through which to return the results of the operation.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Threading.Overlapped"> </xref> klass med den angivna filen position, 32-bitars heltal referensen till en händelse som signaleras när i/o-åtgärden har slutförts och ett gränssnitt som returnerar resultatet av åtgärden.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.Handle%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to get the handle of any managed synchronization event that derives from the <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle> class.
trans-unit.target: Använd <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.Handle%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen för att hämta referensen för alla hanterade synkroniseringshändelsen som härleds från <xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle>klassen.</xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle> </xref:System.Threading.WaitHandle.Handle%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.target: Implementeringen av <xref:System.IAsyncResult>innehåller statusinformation om i/o-åtgärden.</xref:System.IAsyncResult>

trans-unit.source: Pass it to the constructor in the `ar` parameter, and retrieve it later with the <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.AsyncResult%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Överför den till konstruktorn i den `ar` parameter, och hämta den senare med den <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.AsyncResult%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.AsyncResult%2A>

trans-unit.source: Frees the unmanaged memory associated with a native overlapped structure allocated by the <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Pack*> method.
trans-unit.target: Frigör det ohanterade minnet som är associerade med en inbyggd överlappad struktur som allokerats av den <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Pack*>metoden.</xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Pack*>

trans-unit.source: You must call the Free method exactly once on every <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> pointer you receive from the <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Pack%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Du måste anropa metoden ledigt exakt en gång på varje <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped>pekaren som du får från den <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Pack%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Pack%2A> </xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped>

trans-unit.source: If you don't call the Free method, you will leak memory.
trans-unit.target: Om du inte anropa metoden ledigt, kommer du läcker minne.

trans-unit.source: If you call the Free method more than once, memory will be corrupted.
trans-unit.target: Om du anropar metoden ledigt mer än en gång vara minne skadad.

trans-unit.source: A pointer to the <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"></xref> structure to be freed.
trans-unit.target: En pekare till den <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"> </xref> struktur att frigöras.

trans-unit.source: Packs the current instance into a <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"></xref> structure, specifying the delegate to be invoked when the asynchronous I/O operation is complete.
trans-unit.target: Hanteringspaket för den aktuella instansen till en <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"> </xref> struktur, ange ombud som anropas när den asynkrona i/o-åtgärden har slutförts.

trans-unit.source: The unmanaged pointer returned by this method can be passed to the operating system in overlapped I/O operations.
trans-unit.target: Ohanterad pekare som returneras av den här metoden kan skickas till operativsystemet i överlappande i/o-åtgärder.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> structure is fixed in physical memory until <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Unpack%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped>struktur är fast i det fysiska minnet tills <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Unpack%2A>kallas.</xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Unpack%2A> </xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped>

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > The caller is responsible for pinning the buffer.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT] > Anroparen ansvarar för att fästa bufferten.

trans-unit.source: If the application domain is unloaded, however, the handle to the pinned buffer is destroyed and the buffer is released, leaving the I/O operation to write to the freed address.
trans-unit.target: Om programdomänen tas bort, men referensen till Fäst bufferten förstörs och bufferten släpps, lämnar i/o-åtgärden för att skriva till frigjort adressen.

trans-unit.source: For this reason, it is better to use the <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Pack%28System.Threading.IOCompletionCallback%2CSystem.Object%29> method overload, in which the runtime pins the buffer.
trans-unit.target: Därför är det bättre att använda den <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Pack%28System.Threading.IOCompletionCallback%2CSystem.Object%29>metodöverlagringen där körningen PIN-bufferten.</xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Pack%28System.Threading.IOCompletionCallback%2CSystem.Object%29>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Threading.IOCompletionCallback"></xref> delegate that represents the callback method invoked when the asynchronous I/O operation completes.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Threading.IOCompletionCallback"> </xref> delegat som representerar callback-metoden anropas när den asynkrona i/o-åtgärden har slutförts.

trans-unit.source: An unmanaged pointer to a <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"></xref> structure.
trans-unit.target: Ohanterad pekare till en <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"> </xref> struktur.

trans-unit.source: The current <xref href="System.Threading.Overlapped"></xref> has already been packed.
trans-unit.target: Aktuellt <xref href="System.Threading.Overlapped"> </xref> har redan packats.

trans-unit.source: Packs the current instance into a <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"></xref> structure, specifying a delegate that is invoked when the asynchronous I/O operation is complete and a managed object that serves as a buffer.
trans-unit.target: Hanteringspaket för den aktuella instansen till en <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"> </xref> struktur, ange en delegat som anropas när den asynkrona i/o-åtgärden har slutförts och ett hanterat objekt som fungerar som en buffert.

trans-unit.source: The unmanaged pointer returned by this method can be passed to the operating system in overlapped I/O operations.
trans-unit.target: Ohanterad pekare som returneras av den här metoden kan skickas till operativsystemet i överlappande i/o-åtgärder.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> structure is fixed in physical memory until <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Unpack%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped>struktur är fast i det fysiska minnet tills <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Unpack%2A>kallas.</xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Unpack%2A> </xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped>

trans-unit.source: The buffer or buffers specified in `userData` must be the same as those passed to the unmanaged operating system function that performs the asynchronous I/O.
trans-unit.target: Bufferten eller buffertar som anges i `userData` måste vara samma som de som skickas till funktionen ohanterade operativsystemet som utför asynkrona i/o.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The runtime pins the buffer or buffers specified in `userData` for the duration of the I/O operation.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Körningsmiljön PIN-bufferten eller buffertar som anges i `userData` under i/o-åtgärden.

trans-unit.source: If the application domain is unloaded, the runtime keeps the memory pinned until the I/O operation completes.
trans-unit.target: Om programdomänen tas bort, behålls körningsmiljön minne Fäst tills i/o-åtgärden har slutförts.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Threading.IOCompletionCallback"></xref> delegate that represents the callback method invoked when the asynchronous I/O operation completes.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Threading.IOCompletionCallback"> </xref> delegat som representerar callback-metoden anropas när den asynkrona i/o-åtgärden har slutförts.

trans-unit.source: An object or array of objects representing the input or output buffer for the operation.
trans-unit.target: Ett objekt eller en matris med-objekt som representerar den inkommande eller utgående bufferten för åtgärden.

trans-unit.source: Each object represents a buffer, for example an array of bytes.
trans-unit.target: Alla objekt som representerar en buffert, till exempel en matris med byte.

trans-unit.source: An unmanaged pointer to a <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"></xref> structure.
trans-unit.target: Ohanterad pekare till en <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"> </xref> struktur.

trans-unit.source: The current <xref href="System.Threading.Overlapped"></xref> has already been packed.
trans-unit.target: Aktuellt <xref href="System.Threading.Overlapped"> </xref> har redan packats.

trans-unit.source: Unpacks the specified unmanaged <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"></xref> structure into a managed <xref href="System.Threading.Overlapped"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Packar upp den angivna ohanterade <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"> </xref> strukturen i en hanterad <xref href="System.Threading.Overlapped"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> structure is not freed from physical memory until you call the <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Free%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped>struktur inte har frigjorts från det fysiska minnet tills du anropar den <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Free%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Free%2A> </xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped>

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > Using the <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.UnsafePack%2A> method could inadvertently open up a security hole.
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION] > Med hjälp av den <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.UnsafePack%2A>metoden oavsiktligt kan öppna ett säkerhetshål.</xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.UnsafePack%2A>

trans-unit.source: Code access security bases its permission checks on the permissions of all the callers on the stack.
trans-unit.target: Kodåtkomstsäkerhet baserar behörigheterna för alla anropare behörighet kontrollen på stacken.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.UnsafePack%2A> method does not propagate the calling stack.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.UnsafePack%2A>metoden inte spridas anropa stack.</xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.UnsafePack%2A>

trans-unit.source: Malicious code might be able to exploit this to avoid permission checks.
trans-unit.target: Skadlig kod kanske kan utnyttja detta för att undvika behörighet kontroller.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Threading.IOCompletionCallback"></xref> delegate that represents the callback method invoked when the asynchronous I/O operation completes.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Threading.IOCompletionCallback"> </xref> delegat som representerar callback-metoden anropas när den asynkrona i/o-åtgärden har slutförts.

trans-unit.source: An unmanaged pointer to a <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"></xref> structure.
trans-unit.target: Ohanterad pekare till en <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"> </xref> struktur.

trans-unit.source: The current <xref href="System.Threading.Overlapped"></xref> has already been packed.
trans-unit.target: Aktuellt <xref href="System.Threading.Overlapped"> </xref> har redan packats.

trans-unit.source: Packs the current instance into a <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"></xref> structure, specifying the delegate to invoke when the asynchronous I/O operation is complete and the managed object that serves as a buffer.
trans-unit.target: Hanteringspaket för den aktuella instansen till en <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"> </xref> struktur, ange delegaten att anropa när den asynkrona i/o-åtgärden är klar och den hanterade objekt som fungerar som en buffert.

trans-unit.source: Does not propagate the calling stack.
trans-unit.target: Inte att sprida anropa stacken.

trans-unit.source: The unmanaged pointer returned by this method can be passed to the operating system in overlapped I/O operations.
trans-unit.target: Ohanterad pekare som returneras av den här metoden kan skickas till operativsystemet i överlappande i/o-åtgärder.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped> structure is fixed in physical memory until <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Unpack%2A> is called.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped>struktur är fast i det fysiska minnet tills <xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Unpack%2A>kallas.</xref:System.Threading.Overlapped.Unpack%2A> </xref:System.Threading.NativeOverlapped>

trans-unit.source: The buffer or buffers specified in `userData` must be the same as those passed to the unmanaged operating system function that performs the asynchronous I/O.
trans-unit.target: Bufferten eller buffertar som anges i `userData` måste vara samma som de som skickas till funktionen ohanterade operativsystemet som utför asynkrona i/o.

trans-unit.source: The runtime pins the buffer or buffers specified in`userData` for the duration of the I/O operation.
trans-unit.target: PIN-körningsmiljön bufferten eller buffertar som anges i`userData` under i/o-åtgärden.

trans-unit.source: If the application domain is unloaded, the runtime keeps the memory pinned until the I/O operation completes.
trans-unit.target: Om programdomänen tas bort, behålls körningsmiljön minne Fäst tills i/o-åtgärden har slutförts.

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > Using the UnsafePack method could inadvertently open up a security hole.
trans-unit.target: > [!CAUTION] > Med hjälp av UnsafePack metod kan oavsiktligt öppna ett säkerhetshål.

trans-unit.source: Code access security bases its permission checks on the permissions of all the callers on the stack.
trans-unit.target: Kodåtkomstsäkerhet baserar behörigheterna för alla anropare behörighet kontrollen på stacken.

trans-unit.source: The UnsafePack method does not propagate the calling stack.
trans-unit.target: Metoden UnsafePack inte att sprida anropa stacken.

trans-unit.source: Malicious code might be able to exploit this to avoid permission checks.
trans-unit.target: Skadlig kod kanske kan utnyttja detta för att undvika behörighet kontroller.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Threading.IOCompletionCallback"></xref> delegate that represents the callback method invoked when the asynchronous I/O operation completes.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Threading.IOCompletionCallback"> </xref> delegat som representerar callback-metoden anropas när den asynkrona i/o-åtgärden har slutförts.

trans-unit.source: An object or array of objects representing the input or output buffer for the operation.
trans-unit.target: Ett objekt eller en matris med-objekt som representerar den inkommande eller utgående bufferten för åtgärden.

trans-unit.source: Each object represents a buffer, for example an array of bytes.
trans-unit.target: Alla objekt som representerar en buffert, till exempel en matris med byte.

trans-unit.source: An unmanaged pointer to a <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"></xref> structure.
trans-unit.target: Ohanterad pekare till en <xref href="System.Threading.NativeOverlapped"> </xref> struktur.

trans-unit.source: The caller does not have the required permission.
trans-unit.target: Anroparen har inte behörigheten som krävs.

trans-unit.source: The current <xref href="System.Threading.Overlapped"></xref> is already packed.
trans-unit.target: Aktuellt <xref href="System.Threading.Overlapped"> </xref> är redan fullt.
